"Intel is pleased to be working with Sony Online Entertainment to optimize EverQuest for Pentium 4 processor-based systems", said Deborah Conrad, Vice President, Intel Solutions Marketing Group.  "A Pentium 4 processor based system is the ideal EverQuest gaming platform, giving gamers the speed and fluidity they want."</span><br><br>
