<a name="PQN340431"></a>
<br>
<span class="headline">Sony Interview</span><br>
<span class="byline">12/13/01, 21:27 PST | <a href="mailto:kwill@planeteq.com">Kwill</a></span><br><br>
<span class="newsitem"><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/" target="_top">Caster's Realm</a> was fortunate enough to get an <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/viewarticle.asp?Article=3981" target="_top">an exclusive interview</a> with the Sony team about Luclin.<p>Someday maybe I will get an exclusive interview too. /sigh.  I *knew* I should have sent Verant that holiday package sooner! (just kidding).</span><br><br>
